  "description": "<p><b>Note\uff1a</b><br/>Non-Apple branded products,Compatible with iPhone models<br/><br/></p><div><p><b>Overview:</b><br/>MINI GPS TRACKER - - Compact and unobtrusive, this tag will help you keep track of your belongings once you pair it with your smartphone.<br/>BLUETOOTH - Bluetooth 4.0 connection lets you sound an alarm whenever your phone and the tag are separated - great for kids, luggage, pets, and more! Operates using eTracing App (search for it in the Google Play or Apple Store).<br/>CAMERA SHUTTER - Also works as a camera shutter so you can take great selfies and videos.<br/>FEATURES - Standby time 6 months, working range 10m/33ft. Uses one CR2032 coin battery (included)<br/>INDUSTRY LEADING CUSTOMER SUPPORT - You can continue to rely on Electro-Deal to offer the markets most competitive prices, paired with industry leading customer support, and all backed by a one year, full manufacturer\u2019s warranty on new products or a 90 day limited warranty for refurbished products!<br/><br/><b><br/></b></p><p><b>Specifications:</b><br/>Product Type: Bluetooth Tracker<br/>Bluetooth Version: 4.0<br/>Colors: Black, White, Pink, Blue, Green<br/>Working Distance: 10m/33ft (open area)<br/>Battery: CR2032 coin lithium battery<br/>Standby Time: 6 months<br/>Power: 3V/3mA<br/>Size: 3.1\u00d75.2\u00d71.2cm/1.22\u201d\u00d72.05\u201d\u00d70.47\u201d<br/>Compatible with: iPhone 4S/5/5S/5C/6/6S/6 Plus/6S Plus, iPad Mini, iPad 3/4, iPad Air and Android devices with Bluetooth 4.0 (Android 4.3 and newer)</p><p><b><br/>NOTE:</b><br/>1.Product are taken in kind, but because of lighting problems, pictures may have a slight chromatism.<br/>2.Due to the difference between different monitors, the picture may not reflect the actual color of theitem. Please consider this before the purchase.<br/>3.Please allow slight deviation for the measurement data.</p><p><b><br/></b></p><p><b>Package Content:</b></p><p>1 x Anti-theft Device&nbsp;</p></div><div date-role=\"nav-panel\"><div data-role=\"nav-detail-item\"><ul><li><p align=\"justify\"><img alt=\"10\" src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/17175456/2406050132240324400.jpg\"/><img alt=\"11\" src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/17175456/2406050132240325400.jpg\"/></p><p align=\"justify\"><img alt=\"21\" src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/17175456/2406050132240326100.jpg\"/><img alt=\"30\" src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/17175456/2406050132240327000.jpg\"/><img alt=\"31\" src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/17175456/2406050132240328100.jpg\"/><br/></p><p align=\"justify\">Protocole de Communication: smartphone Bluetooth 4.0 (android 4.3 et mise \u00e0 niveau)</p><p align=\"justify\">Distance de travail: &lt;= 25 m (environnement ext\u00e9rieur)</p><p align=\"justify\">Batterie: pile au lithium CR2032, dure environ 6 mois</p><p align=\"justify\">T\u00e9l\u00e9phone Compatible: iPhone4S/5/5 S/5C, iPad Mini, iTouch 5, iPad 3/4, iPad Air et syst\u00e8me android et Bluetooth</p><p align=\"justify\">Dans ces circonstances,</p><p align=\"justify\"><img alt=\"1\" src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/17175456/2406050132240329100.jpg\"/><img alt=\"2\" src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/17175456/2406050132250320100.jpg\"/><img alt=\"3\" src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/17175456/2406050132250321000.jpg\"/><img alt=\"4\" src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/17175456/2406050132250321500.jpg\"/></p><p align=\"justify\"><br/></p><p align=\"justify\"><img alt=\"9\" src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/17175456/2406050132250322500.jpg\"/></p><p align=\"justify\"><img alt=\"1\" src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/17175456/2406050132240329100.jpg\"/><img alt=\"2\" src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/17175456/2406050132250320100.jpg\"/></p><p align=\"justify\">Troisi\u00e8mement, le retardateur Bluetooth anti-perte caract\u00e9ristiques:</p><p align=\"justify\">1, connexion Bluetooth de t\u00e9l\u00e9phone portable, fonction de recherche bidirectionnelle, peut \u00eatre connect\u00e9 \u00e0 10 dispositif anti-perte;</p><p align=\"justify\">2, dans l'\u00e9tat connect\u00e9, dispositif anti-perte que d\u00e9finir la plage Bluetooth, les t\u00e9l\u00e9phones mobiles et alarme anti-perte en m\u00eame temps alarme;</p><p align=\"justify\">3, sur le t\u00e9l\u00e9phone peut v\u00e9rifier la carte de l'emplacement de l'appareil anti-perte;</p><p align=\"justify\">4, pour fournir une fonction de non-interf\u00e9rence, vous pouvez d\u00e9finir une p\u00e9riode de silence, pour emp\u00eacher le travail et d'autres interf\u00e9rences de temps importantes;</p><p align=\"justify\">5, par la prise de vue de t\u00e9l\u00e9phone portable anti-perte de contr\u00f4le, retardateur \u00e0 distance.</p><p align=\"justify\">6, par l'enregistrement de t\u00e9l\u00e9phone portable anti-perte de contr\u00f4le.</p><p align=\"justify\"><img alt=\"5\" src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/17175456/2406050132250323600.jpg\"/><img alt=\"6\" src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/17175456/2406050132250324300.jpg\"/></p><p align=\"justify\"><br/></p><p align=\"justify\"><img alt=\"7\" src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/17175456/2406050132250325300.jpg\"/><img alt=\"12\" src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/17175456/2406050132250326700.jpg\"/><br/></p></li></ul></div></div>",
